OL,3,CPolice investigation into death of
OL,4,CAlice Webb set to close
OL,6,FA police investigation into the death
OL,7,Fof Alice Webb, a mum from
OL,8,FGloucestershire, is set to close,
OL,9,Fpolice said on Tuesday.
OL,11,FThe Major Crime Investigation Team's
OL,12,Fwork will end after the death of the
OL,13,Fforce's main suspect, Gloucestershire
OL,14,FPolice told ITV News in a statement.
OL,16,FWebb, a mother of five, became unwell
OL,17,Fduring a cosmetic procedure in
OL,18,FSeptember 2024 and later died in
OL,19,Fhospital.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
