OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1771974352
OL,3,CPolice investigation into death of
OL,4,CAlice Webb set to close
OL,6,FShe had had a liquid Brazilian Butt
OL,7,FLift, which involves filler injections
OL,8,Finto the bum to make it look bigger.
OL,10,FA man and woman were arrested at the
OL,11,Ftime on suspicion of manslaughter. The
OL,12,Fwoman was later told she faced no
OL,13,Ffurther police action, and the man
OL,14,Fremained on bail while the police
OL,15,Finvestigation took place.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
