CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1771974352
OL,3,CPolice investigation into death of
OL,4,CAlice Webb set to close
OL,6,FMetropolitan Police officers and
OL,7,Fparamedics found Parke dead in a hotel
OL,8,Fin Canary Wharf, London. Initial
OL,9,Finquiries suggest Parke may have had a
OL,10,Fcosmetic procedure before he died,
OL,11,Faccording to officials.
OL,13,FHis death remains unexplained. A post-
OL,14,Fmortem examination is due to be
OL,15,Fcarried out.
OL,17,FTwo people, a 43-year-old man and a 52-
OL,18,Fyear-old woman, have been arrested on
OL,19,Fsuspicion of manslaughter in
OL,20,Fconnection with his death. Both have
OL,21,Fbeen bailed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
