PN,31506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1771974352
OL,3,CPolice investigation into death of
OL,4,CAlice Webb set to close
OL,6,F"Alice had become unwell following a
OL,7,Fcosmetic procedure, and two people
OL,8,Fwere arrested on suspicion of
OL,9,Fmanslaughter in connection with her
OL,10,Fdeath.
OL,12,F"A woman was later told she faced no
OL,13,Ffurther police action, and a man
OL,14,Fremained on police bail while further
OL,15,Fenquiries were taking place.
OL,17,F"We have been informed that the man
OL,18,Fwho was on police bail died recently,
OL,19,Fand therefore the criminal
OL,20,Finvestigation will close as no charges
OL,21,Fcan be brought.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
