PN,31507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1771974352
OL,3,CPolice investigation into death of
OL,4,CAlice Webb set to close
OL,6,F"Police enquiries will continue on
OL,7,Fbehalf of the coroner, and an inquest
OL,8,Fwill take place in due course to try
OL,9,Fand establish what happened.
OL,11,F"Alice's family has been updated, and
OL,12,Fwe hope the inquest will enable
OL,13,FAlice's family to have the answers
OL,14,Fthey deserve."
